Please answer these questions before submitting pull request

- Why submit this pull request?
We have got a lot of error logs like: org.elasticsearch.action.ActionRequestValidationException: Validation Failed: 1: id is too long, must be no longer than 512 bytes but was: 685;

Without the detailed log, we cannot do improvement for the endpoint names or find out whether SkyWalking has a bug or not.

First, I provide more readable codes for #2926 fix.
Then, as people are asking for bootstrap class enhancing, so I provided this as an optional mechanism. I am still hesitating whether we should accept plugin for bootstrap class, such as `java.net.URLConnection`

@ascrutae @candyleer We should test by using this to enhance some class in `rt.jar`. Please verify.
